{"id": "art-25124", "label": "Art. 25124", "title": "Art. 25124", "slug": "art-25124", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_766004274\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1698\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_766004274\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>24</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1499851819\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1697\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1499851819\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Administratorii\nsau membrii directoratului <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncare urmeaz&#259; a participa la fuziune întocmesc un proiect comun de fuziune\ntransfrontalier&#259; care trebuie s&#259; cuprind&#259; cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1088311789\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1696\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1088311789\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)forma juridic&#259; de societate, firma/denumirea <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sediul social ale tuturor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nparticipante la fuziune;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1448276036\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1695\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1448276036\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)forma juridic&#259; de societate, firma/denumirea <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sediul social ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nnou-constituite, dac&#259; este cazul;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_758139656\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1694\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_758139656\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)<span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> aloc&#259;rii\nde <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social la societatea\nabsorbant&#259; sau la societatea nou-constituit&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_326274729\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1693\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_326274729\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)rata de schimb a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncuantumul eventualelor <span class=SpellE>pl&#259;&#355;i</span> în numerar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_771384659\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1692\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_771384659\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)data de la care <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span> sociale sau alte titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social prev&#259;zute la lit. c) dau <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span>\ndreptul de a participa la beneficii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> orice <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;ii</span> speciale care afecteaz&#259; acest drept;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1528250746\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1691\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1528250746\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)drepturile acordate de c&#259;tre societatea\nabsorbant&#259; sau nou-constituit&#259; <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social care\nconfer&#259; drepturi speciale sau m&#259;surile propuse în <span class=SpellE>privin&#355;a</span>\nacestora;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2048668327\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1690\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2048668327\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)orice avantaje speciale acordate administratorilor ori\ndirectorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, membrilor consiliului de supraveghere ori\ndirectoratului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1631297485\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1689\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1631297485\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind\nevaluarea activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivelor transferate <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante sau <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nnou-constituite;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2103250678\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1688\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2103250678\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)data de la care <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;iile</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbite sunt considerate din\npunct de vedere contabil ca <span class=SpellE>apar&#355;inând</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante sau nou-constituite;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_355288337\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1687\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_355288337\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>j)<span class=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span> fuziunii\nasupra <span class=SpellE>for&#355;ei</span> de munc&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1323126980\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1686\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1323126980\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>k)data <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iilor</span>\nfinanciare ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> participante\ncare au fost folosite pentru a se stabili <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nfuziunii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1087881444\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1685\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1087881444\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>l)dac&#259; este cazul, <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span>\ncu privire la procedurile de stabilire a particip&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a altor <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nde implicare a acestora în activitatea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nabsorbante sau nou-constituite;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_330822933\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1684\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_330822933\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>m)<span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ul</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social pentru <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\nîn care <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nexercit&#259; dreptul de retragere din societate, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nadresa de e-mail la care <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> pot transmite\n<span class=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span> de retragere;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_232738429\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1683\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_232738429\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>n)orice <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> acordate\ncreditorilor, precum <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> reale sau\npersonale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_339946371\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1682\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_339946371\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)La proiectul comun de fuziune transfrontalier&#259;\nprev&#259;zut la alin. (1) va fi anexat proiectul actului constitutiv al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ce urmeaz&#259; a fi <span\nclass=SpellE>înfiin&#355;at&#259;</span>, respectiv proiectul de act\nmodificator al actului constitutiv al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nabsorbante, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span>\nfinanciare întocmite în vederea fuziunii, aprobate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nauditate potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, ce nu pot fi\nmai vechi de 6 luni înainte de data proiectului de fuziune.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_96263326\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1681\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_96263326\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;ase</span> s&#259;pt&#259;mâni înainte de data întrunirii\nadun&#259;rii generale convocate s&#259; aprobe fuziunea transfrontalier&#259;,\nproiectul comun de fuziune transfrontalier&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nanexele acestuia se pun la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>, cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\nîn format electronic, prin <span class=SpellE>afi&#351;are</span> pe pagina de\ninternet a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>28</sup> alin. (3), sau\nprin transmitere pe cale electronic&#259;, <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ii</span>\nprimind <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> o notificare în conformitate cu art.\n251<sup>28</sup> alin. (1).</span></p>"}